{
    "status": "live",
    "tags": [
        "service:store-discounts",
        "team:discounts",
        "env:service-catalog-course"
    ],
    "locations": [
        "aws:ca-central-1",
        "aws:eu-west-1"
    ],
    "message": "```\n{{#is_alert}}\n# The Storedog discounts service is taking longer than expected to load\nReview the current state and [declare an Incident](https://app.datadoghq.com/incidents/new).\n\n## Resources\n- [Discount Service Incident Response doc](https://storedog.atlassian.net/wiki/)\n- [store-discounts service ownership details](https://app.datadoghq.com/services?currentTopTab=Ownership&env=service-catalog-course&hostGroup=&selectedService=store-discounts)\n\n{{/is_alert}} \n\n{{#is_recovery}}\n# The Storedog discounts service has recovered from high latency\nReview [Incidents](https://app.datadoghq.com/incidents) and resolve as needed.\n\n## Action needed\n- Create Postmortem Notebook from Incident\n- Schedule Postmortem review\n\n{{/is_recovery}} \n```",
    "name": "Test discount service reponse",
    "type": "api",
    "subtype": "http",
    "config": {
        "request": {
            "url": "https://{{ HOSTNAME }}-{{ DISCOUNTS_PORT }}-{{ PARTICIPANT_ID }}.env.play.instruqt.com/discount",
            "method": "GET"
        },
        "assertions": [
            {
                "operator": "lessThan",
                "type": "responseTime",
                "target": 6000
            },
            {
                "operator": "is",
                "type": "statusCode",
                "target": 200
            },
            {
                "operator": "is",
                "property": "content-type",
                "type": "header",
                "target": "application/json"
            },
            {
                "operator": "validatesJSONPath",
                "type": "body",
                "target": {
                    "operator": "isNot",
                    "targetValue": "",
                    "jsonPath": "$[0].code"
                }
            }
        ],
        "configVariables": [
            {
                "type": "global",
                "id": "foo",
                "name": "HOSTNAME"
            },
            {
                "type": "global",
                "id": "foo",
                "name": "DISCOUNTS_PORT"
            },
            {
                "type": "global",
                "id": "foo",
                "name": "PARTICIPANT_ID"
            }
        ]
    },
    "options": {
        "monitor_options": {
            "renotify_interval": 0
        },
        "httpVersion": "any",
        "min_location_failed": 1,
        "min_failure_duration": 0,
        "tick_every": 60
    }
}